Expense Tracker (Flask)

Overview
A simple Expense Tracker web app built with Flask.  
Users can add expenses with amounts, view them in a list, see the running total, and delete individual items.  

---

Features
-  Add a new expense with a name and amount  
-  Delete expenses individually  
-  Amounts formatted to two decimal places (e.g., `Â£50.05`)  
-  Displays the total sum of all expenses  
-  Responsive form design (works on small screens)  

---

Tech Stack
- Backend: Python (Flask)  
- Frontend: HTML, CSS (custom styling)  
- Templating: Jinja2  


